Excellent place to stay!
I come to Da Nang once every year and have been staying here for 4 years in a row. A La Carte is my favorite hotel here in Da Nang. The property is in a great location, is very clean, and staff is the best. The rooftop bar/pool, the spa, the room service food, the buffet/restaurants and kind staff make it an excellent stay every time.
