Mansur M wrote a review Jul 2019
India455 contributions38 helpful votes
Great Location and Decor, Fantastic View of Ocean and Beach from Balcony
The hotel is located at the rightest location in Da Nang City, Plenty of street food stalls just at stone throw distance, Rooms with Ocean View Balcony are amazing, Breakfast is good and enough to choose from, Room Interior are unique specially the batroom shower enclosure in between the middle of room. BE CAREFUL OF BATH MIXTURE, Its get very hot and could burn your skin. Look for HOT sticker placed near the water regulator. Look at pictures attached to have a view of Room, balcony, Beach, The room entrance is through a huge living room with a tiny powder room and another Balcony with a cloth drying hanger trolley. Only one star less in my review because of damp smell inside room. everything else is unique.
Date of stay: June 2019
