Jude W wrote a review Jul 2019
Melbourne, Australia16 contributions21 helpful votes
Great Hotel Excellent customer service
We stayed here for three nights. Had the best time ever. The staff are super friendly and helpful. Also have a guest service team who helped my wife after a burn from a motor cycle exhaust. THAO from guest service even came up to our room to dress the wound. The hotel is located in the middle of all the action on Da nang beach and close to all the restaurants shopping and massage places. The rooms are very clean and tidy. Ours overlooked the ocean with amazing views. Breakfast is very good with a choice of Asian and continental. The roof top bar is where the pool is and has views of Da nang. There is a a lot of entertainment just opposite the hotel which does get a bit loud sometimes but you just need to get with the beat to enjoy. I would however suggest a room on the higher…
