Great hotel
I had a lovely experience staying in Ala Carte hotel Da Nang. The room was clean and beautiful ocean view And delicious breakfast meal. Great customer service from the reception especially the supervisor receptionist Vuong he was great and very welcoming. Unfortunately, it was a noisy place for us to stay. We couldn’t sleep at night due to the karaoke noise and street noise. Overall, it was a great stay.
